Ms Roseline Yuhe, Proprietor and Lead teacher, Berries World School Bwari, FCT has tasked parents on home schooling their children and wards to help them succeed and further improve their intellect. Yuhe spoke in an interview with the News Agency of Nigeria (NAN) on Tuesday in Abuja. According to her, having smart and intelligent children needs more than limiting learning to the walls of the school but practical efforts from parents. She said that if parents helped their children believe that they could learn and grow their intelligence, then the child or children truly could appreciate it. 